.SH "NAME"
paxctl\-ng \- get or set the PaX flags for both PT_PAX and XT_PAX markings
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR [\-PpEeMmRrXxSs] [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR \-Z [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR \-z [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR \-C [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR \-c [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
\&\fBpaxctl-ng\fR \-d [\-v] \s-1ELF\s0
.PP
